{"id":"api/core/ViewChild","title":"ViewChild","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/ViewChild\", \"name\": \"ViewChild\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/di.ts#L450-L456\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"viewchild\">ViewChild<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#viewchild\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8kpd59enh4ftilvb1ryettnmi\">屬性裝飾器，用於設定一個檢視查詢。變更檢測器會在檢視的 DOM 中查詢能對應上該選擇器的第一個元素或指令。如果檢視的 DOM 發生了變化，出現了對應該選擇器的新的子節點，該屬性就會被更新。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/ViewChild#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"958p250s4a4gqxdqtti9sbuqo\"><strong>元資料屬性</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"59spbvqm8cpa6royeh8occk6l\"><strong>selector</strong> - 要查詢的指令類型或名稱。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7r4y6m3967yuqbqr6ux3c6g6b\"><strong>read</strong> - 用於從查詢到的元素中讀取不同的令牌。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ci9jpz7uvh0pzg725tr4mruh4\"><strong>static</strong> - \n<code>true</code>表示在變更檢測執行之前解析查詢結果，\n<code>false</code>表示在變更檢測執行之後解析。預設為\n<code>false</code>。</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"f08e65jh4yx0pw6hnbokpkhry\">支援下列選擇器：。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"330yjla87rxyroyq6xsq9o9op\">任何帶有 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> 或 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a></code> 裝飾器的類別</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"71pfafm8id9dl70bu1nur90a3\">字串形式的範本引用變數（比如可以使用 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>('cmp')</code> 來查詢 <code>&lt;my-component #cmp&gt;&lt;/my-component&gt;</code></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dfektnpoldzg285gdv5plxd0r\">元件樹中任何當前元件的子元件所定義的提供者（比如 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>(SomeService) someService: SomeService</code> ）</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bzs8bheoqd9qo6c2w3pc4bwgj\">任何透過字串令牌定義的提供者（比如 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>('someToken') someTokenVal: any</code>）</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3oaiue9u1hf61rha4q20u88um\"><code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code>（比如可以用 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>(<a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a>) template;</code> 來查詢 <code>&lt;ng-template&gt;&lt;/ng-template&gt;</code>）</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"30xysbii0fi7zioc9r2fhgsm9\"><code>read</code> 支援以下值：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"330yjla87rxyroyq6xsq9o9op\">任何帶有 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a></code> 或 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a></code> 裝飾器的類別</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"coewcx1n8w3uha9rpq3nc07sb\">在此查詢的 <code>selector</code> 對應的元件注入器上定義的任何提供程式</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4a5dny1l0sl0prfh4x77ge8cs\">透過字串標記定義的任何提供程式（例如 <code>{provide: 'token', useValue: 'val'}</code>）</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bwws9nk3malja82otpkhgtiog\"><code><a href=\"api/core/TemplateRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">TemplateRef</a></code>、<code><a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a></code> 和 <code><a href=\"api/core/ViewContainerRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewContainerRef</a></code></li>\n</ul>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a53c2co998clebdw98hbngj7i\">動態查詢和靜態查詢的區別：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7nz5ip02mzaraf76tejl4jciz\">動態查詢（\n<code><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a>: false</code>） - 查詢在呼叫\n<code>ngAfterViewInit()</code>回呼之前解析。結果將根據檢視的更改而更新，例如更改\n<code><a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a></code>和\n<code><a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code>區塊。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ddatpjd1c6w3xgh0f0agjgqc3\">靜態查詢（\n<code><a href=\"api/upgrade/static\" class=\"code-anchor\">static</a>: true</code>） - 查詢在檢視建立後但在變更檢測執行之前解析（在呼叫\n<code>ngOnInit()</code>回呼之前）。結果不會隨著檢視的更改而更新，例如更改\n<code><a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a></code>和\n<code><a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code>區塊。</li>\n</ul>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4vkewx5ewsm6boupe095zhjr3\">進一步的訊息可在\n<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild#usage-notes\">使用說明...</a>中找到。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"decorator-options\">\n  <h2 id=\"options\">選項<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n</section>\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h3 id=\"example-1\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"51744ssk6qm7vaem8fmwyfc9m\">範例 1<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#example-1\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example path=\"core/di/ts/viewChild/view_child_example.ts\" region=\"Component\">\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>, <a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({selector: 'pane'})\nexport class Pane {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>() id!: string;\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'example-app',\n  template: `\n    &lt;pane id=\"1\" *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"shouldShow\"&gt;&lt;/pane&gt;\n    &lt;pane id=\"2\" *<a href=\"api/common/NgIf\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngIf</a>=\"!shouldShow\"&gt;&lt;/pane&gt;\n\n    &lt;button (click)=\"toggle()\"&gt;Toggle&lt;/button&gt;\n\n    &lt;div&gt;Selected: {{ selectedPane }}&lt;/div&gt;\n  `,\n})\nexport class ViewChildComp {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>(Pane)\n  set pane(v: Pane) {\n    setTimeout(() =&gt; {\n      this.selectedPane = v.id;\n    }, 0);\n  }\n  selectedPane: string = '';\n  shouldShow = true;\n  toggle() {\n    this.shouldShow = !this.shouldShow;\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<h3 id=\"example-2\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5myjpo365s6azfpu6fempyl94\">例子 2<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewChild#example-2\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example path=\"core/di/ts/viewChild/view_child_howto.ts\" region=\"HowTo\">\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterViewInit</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>, <a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>, <a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({selector: 'child-directive'})\nclass ChildDirective {}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({selector: 'someCmp', templateUrl: 'someCmp.html'})\nclass SomeCmp implements <a href=\"api/core/AfterViewInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">AfterViewInit</a> {\n  @<a href=\"api/core/ViewChild\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewChild</a>(ChildDirective) child!: ChildDirective;\n\n  ngAfterViewInit() {\n    // child is set\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/NgComponentOutlet\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/core\n - api/core/Query\n - api/core/ViewContainerRef\n - api/core/afterNextRender\n - api/core/afterRender\n - api/core/ng-template\n - errors/NG0503\n - guide/change-detection-skipping-subtrees\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/deprecations\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n - guide/property-binding\n - guide/signal-queries\n - guide/ssr\n - guide/static-query-migration\n - guide/testing-components-scenarios\n - guide/update-to-version-17\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common/NgFor\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/core\n - api/core/AfterViewInit\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/ElementRef\n - api/core/Input\n - api/core/TemplateRef\n - api/core/ViewChild#description\n - api/core/ViewChild#example-1\n - api/core/ViewChild#example-2\n - api/core/ViewChild#options\n - api/core/ViewChild#usage-notes\n - api/core/ViewChild#viewchild\n - api/core/ViewContainerRef\n - api/upgrade/static\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/di.ts#L450-L456\n-->"}